    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#created_expression>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Indicates that an activity created an Expression.\nThis property is mostly here for compatibility with FRBRoo, but implementations would prefer using created_a_realization_of to link to the Work level.\nThis could indicate that some Expressions of a Work were created by the activity, and some others were translated afterwards."@en .
