    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#has_another_publication>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Inverse of \"is_another_publication_of\"."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#is_part_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Indicates a work in which this one is physically included. Covers the case of text included in an Official Journal, or an article included in a text. For the notion of conceptual/temporal inclusion, use eli:is_member_of."@en .
