    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#countersigned_by>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>	"countersigned by"@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#ensures_implementation_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalResource> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#Language>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10240> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#ActivityType>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf>	<http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/E55_Type> .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10083>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalExpression> .
