    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalValue>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#equivalentClass>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10244> .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10222>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10221> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalValue-unofficial>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo>	"created in v1.0"@en .
