    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10198>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10107>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#first>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#Manifestation> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#Format>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo>	"modified in v1.3" .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#is_subject_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Thing> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#based_on_a_realization_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Indicates that an Activity used some Work .The works are seen as the \\\"input\\\" of the activity.\n\nExample : the work of a commitee \\\"used\\\" a specific version of the draft as input to produce an opinion document.\n\nNote : the naming \\\"used a realization of\\\" is taken from FRBRoo. Since a work is an idea, existing only in people's mind, an activity cannot be simply said to have \\\"used\\\" a work, but really \\\"used an expression of this work\\\"."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#has_another_publication>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>	"has another publication"@en .
    <https://www.iana.org/assignments/media-types/application/xml>	<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel>	"application/xml" .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#implements>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo>	"modified in v1.1"@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#legislative_process_work_type>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"The type of a legislative process work. The list of possible types need to be defined by each Member States.\n\nExample : \\\"Opinition from the economic commitee\\\", \\\"Impact analysis\\\", \\\"text of the bill\\\", \\\"debate recording\\\", \\\"amendment\\\"."@en .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10213>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10212> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#InForce-notInForce>	<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition>	"Indicates that a legal resource is currently not in force."@en .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10192>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
