    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#executed>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#ForeseenActivity> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#ParticipationRole>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"The role of an Agent in a Participation, e.g. \"Rapporteur\", \"Shadow Rapporteur\", etc."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#implementation_ensured_by>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#LegalResource> .
