    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#AdministrativeArea>	<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#historyNote>	"v1.3 : Updated the link to EU vocabularies website in the definition.\nStarting from v1.1, the values for administrative areas can be taken from the Administrative Territorial Unit table published of the EU Publications Office."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#ensures_implementation_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>	"ensures implementation of"@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#foresees_consolidation_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Indicates a LegalResource already published that the future law, if adopted, will consolidates. Readers should refer to the definition of the eli:consoidates property.\nNote the legal impacts can change in successive versions of the same document."@en .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10261>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#onProperty>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#activity_start_date> .
