    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#is_realized_by>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Relates a work to an expression of this work in the form of a \"sequence of signs\" (typically alpha-numeric characters in a legal context). Inverse of \"realizes\"."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#description>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label>	"description"@en .
