    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#first_date_entry_in_force>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10204> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#ProcessStatus>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"The overall status of a legislative process. ELI-DL provides 3 possible values : Ongoing, Successful, or Abandonned. Other values can be defined by implementors."@en .
