    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"An ontology to describe legislation, based on the FRBR model, that encodes the ELI metadata fields.\nSee the classes \"LegalResource\", \"LegalExpression\" and \"Format\" as entry points.\nInterested readers can find more information about ELI on the ELI register at http://eurlex.europa.eu/eli and on the Office of Publications vocabularies website at https://op.europa.eu/en/web/eu-vocabularies/eli."@en .
