    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10158>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#unionOf>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10160> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#process_type>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"The type of a process. The type of a process often determine the workflow being followed to create the law.\n\nThe list of possible values need to be defined by each Member State.\n\nExample : \\\"Projet de loi\\\", \\\"Proposition de loi\\\", \\\"Revision of the Constitution\\\", \\\"Public Bill\\\"."@en .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10161>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#unionOf>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10163> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#media_type>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#format> .
