    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#is_answered_in>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#answers_to> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#is_adopted_in>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#adopts> .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10214>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
    <http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10175>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#rest>	<http://www.example.org/id/.well-known/genid/vb10174> .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#includes_amendment>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#inverseOf>	<http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#amendment_included_in> .
