    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#includes_amendment>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Indicate an amendment that was passed and included in this version of the legislation draft. This property is meant to refer to individual amendments that have been voted to be integrated in the text of the law."@en .
