    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#foresees_execution_of>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Indicates a LegalResource already published of which the future law, if adopted, will ensure the execution. Readers should refer to the definition of the eli:ensures_execution_of property.\nNote the legal impacts can change in successive versions of the same document."@en .
