    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#refers_to>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"Deprecated. This was generalised in the ELI ontology. Use eli:refers_to instead."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#FormatTypeTable>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"A set of types for a Format.\nELI includes a list of values for this table.\nThis should contain user-oriented types to dinstinguish e.g. authentic PDF from scanned PDF from generated-on-the-fly PDF; or e.g. XML in a standard (AkomaNtoso) format vs. XML in a proprietary format."@en .
    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/ontology#commences>	<http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type>	<http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
