    <http://data.europa.eu/eli/eli-draft-legislation-ontology#process_id>	<http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment>	"An identifier for the process. This is meant to capture how the process is identified by law makers. A process can have multiple identifiers for different institutions, e.g. an identifier for the government, and an identifier for the parliament.\n\nNote that a subproperty process_external_id exists to capture the identifier of another institution, depending on the point of view."@en .
